Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.98,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}"Land Submarine of Love and Fishing"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.84,0:00:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think Ozu is an asshole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.23,0:00:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He farts the moment before the matsutake rice enters my mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.33,0:00:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he mixes all the wasabi in the dip and eats the soba like nothing is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.14,0:00:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd definitely meet him during a walk after dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.47,0:00:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He puts one part coffee in four parts milk,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.94,0:00:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he grabs and buys books from the bottom of the stack.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.49,0:00:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he walks, he totters,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.45,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his face is generally unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way he skilfully drags people along is also unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.77,0:00:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, has that guy ever truly gone fishing before?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.05,0:00:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And so I arrived at the Kamogawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.67,0:00:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Ozu hasn't shown up.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.40,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fad(400,0)}"I'm going to meet up with Akashi-san. I'll be right back.\N -Ozu"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you planning to meet her?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.65,0:00:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A harpoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.11,0:00:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.13,0:00:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing as in to catch a fish with a hook through the mouth just to return it back to water?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.06,0:00:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.12,0:00:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a hook, a hook!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.23,0:01:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sticks in the mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive not properly cooking and eating what you fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.37,0:01:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would normally eat what you fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.87,0:01:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.37,0:01:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I'm dealing with Ozu now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.78,0:01:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I was being chased.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.34,0:01:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It felt like we met eye to eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.63,0:01:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.02,0:01:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a figurehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.17,0:01:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.95,0:01:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, to the Land submarine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.06,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Land submarine?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.02,0:01:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That harpoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the cause of my haze.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.91,0:01:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For extracting that for me, I am-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.17,0:01:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.45,0:01:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.09,0:01:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning to abduct Akashi-san. What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:01:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's "he?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.09,0:01:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you get him with that harpoon, captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.41,0:01:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see. The only person that can save her is me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.60,0:02:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see that just now? The captain abandoned this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.60,0:02:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think a man who abandons his duty can save Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.12,0:02:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that really alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As it stands, that captain will do as he pleases,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and only the captain can move this boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.45,0:02:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do with this captainless boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.62,0:02:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The future will change based on your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.42,0:02:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Future?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of my future...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:37.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raise the anchor! Set sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're after Akashi-san's bus, get ahead of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.68,0:02:55.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite the sharp one,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.65,0:02:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.65,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Captain?"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a subtle change in Akashi-san's movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Subtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akashi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.28,0:03:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I promised Ozu I'd go fishing with him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.92,0:03:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moth-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, captain, do you fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fishing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, what, what, what's that noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.98,0:03:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the clay pipes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:43.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.95,0:03:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.18,0:03:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The new deputy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.61,0:03:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the captain, I'm your superior!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instruction manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\c&H010101&\3c&H6E6C90&\pos(596,303)\frz19.643}"*Please read before use"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't help but to grab it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.60,0:04:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another new deputy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.97,0:04:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt it was a quick change.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,User manual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instructions for the land submarine were written inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H0B0B0B&\c&HBFBFBF&}"How to operate"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Deputy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.30,0:04:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should read that carefully from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That man began talking as if he had memorized everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems this boat can advance effortlessly in solid matter by changing its surroundings into water-like substances.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moment we hit clay pipes,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.38,0:04:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was dismissed from my duty as captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.97,0:04:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that, more importantly, Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's holding the harpoon alone and heading this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to pierce this boat with the harpoon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The torpedoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The torpedoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I see. I had the same thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.33,0:04:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking my idea, but I'll turn a blind eye this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.06,0:04:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go head and use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.34,0:04:54.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Torpedo, loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, at that moment, didn't care about Akashi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to change these poor surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! Please shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.04,0:05:15.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.99,0:05:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't this God's rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to become drippy like a towel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.34,0:05:43.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... not Ozu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.23,0:05:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Your cleared heart discovered this God's rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I returned to Kamo River with Ozu waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.75,0:06:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I waited for quite a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:06.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've fished more than enough today, so I'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I also invited Akashi-san, but she couldn't make it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.36,0:06:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Instead, she said she wanted to give you this memo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.95,0:06:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm writing a report today, so I can't participate in fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.07,0:06:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish you could catch that I'd be glad to receive:
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.82,0:06:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Octopus and tuna?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.82,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just where did Ozu say we were going to fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that matter, what did he catch today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.08,0:06:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This may be a place to philosophize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.08,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that story?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.97,0:06:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't the least bit interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably a more or less true story that did not involve us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done talking!
